videos.description: UCF's Adrian Killins Jr. runs 15 yards into the end zone for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Killins gives UCF first TD of game

videos.description: UCF's McKenzie Milton connects with Dredrick Snelson for a 14-yard Knights touchdown.
videos.headline: Milton finds Snelson for 14-yard TD

videos.description: Otis Anderson squeezes into the end zone for a 4-yard UCF touchdown.
videos.headline: UCF continues to cruise with 4-yard TD

videos.description: At 315 pounds, DL Trysten Hill comes in as a fullback and runs in a 1-yard touchdown to give UCF a 33-10 lead.
videos.headline: 315-pounder punches in UCF TD

videos.description: McKenzie Milton connects with Tre Nixon for a 30-yard touchdown, Milton's second passing TD of the night.
videos.headline: McKenzie Milton rips 30-yard TD

videos.description: Otis Anderson finds a hole and runs in for a 30-yard touchdown to put UCF up 48-13.
videos.headline: UFC adds to lead with 30-yard TD
